	* mgetty.c: removed #include <ioctl.h> (not needed anymore)

Mon Apr 25 11:59:35 1994  Gert Doering  (gert@greenie)

	* mgetty.c (main): on a system with a two-user-limit, don't make a
	"dialout" utmp entry

	* released 0.20

